transcripts: Medina with priority was going to roll in , to set up work now rolling in stalling for the barrel, now starting to drive this section , driving away Medina reappears down the line and now goes for the ally-oke  landing in the flats into a lay back  and he will recover. [Crowd cheering.] Yeah I'm just stoked, I'm so happy, yeah I'm really happy to make this final with him he's a good friend of mine, and yeah so happy!
